# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Contact form — Web3Forms access key (PUBLIC by design; safe to expose in the
# built site). See CONTACT_FORM_MAINTENANCE.md for full setup and testing.
#
# 1. Go to https://web3forms.com and create an access key registered to the
#    delivery inbox (ksarin@stanford.edu).
# 2. Copy this file to `.env.local` (which is gitignored) and paste the key
#    below. Rebuild. Leaving it empty keeps the form in safe "draft" mode
#    (it validates input but never claims a message was sent).
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_KEY=
